{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Blend_It is a minimalist, comfortable puzzle game.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your goal is to combine the simple figures provided to fit the images presented.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>a puzzle game with a new mechanism</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Blend_It is a game that uses only black and white colors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">White has a value of 1, and black has a value of 0.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can edit the combination by selecting shapes, selecting multiplication, addition, and subtraction operations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Think of colors as numbers, use operators, layering shapes to create new shapes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>a constant challenge</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are currently a total of 100 stages for Blend_It. (We're still updating it.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you have completed the 100th stage, the infinite mode created by AI will be lifted.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience new stages constantly through Infinite Mode!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322380/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733224140","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322380/page.bg.jpg?t=1733224140","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322380/badcda1e46d77a7ed5f9fb7d9986f57d58fe7acb/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733224140","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322380/badcda1e46d77a7ed5f9fb7d9986f57d58fe7acb/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733224140","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Blend_It is a minimalist, comfortable puzzle game.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your goal is to c